    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make Carers Allowance equivalent to a fair wage & allow multiple claims",
        "additional_details": "For example, a family with 2 disabled children affects a parent being able to work part-time or full-time but current rules of claiming for 1 cared person does not cover the carer financially.\r\n\r\nCarers are grossly underpaid and the system does not recognised when a carer cares for more than one person.",
        "background": "Make carers allowance equivalent to a fair wage and allow multiple carers allowance (with a limit) where more than 1 person is cared for. ",
